PrecisAppointment of WAYNE ADAMS, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, RICHARD BINDER, of Inuvik, Northwest Territories, JULIE CRUIKSHANK, of Vancouver, British Columbia, JEAN DUPUIS, of Kuujjuak, Quebec, and PETER JOHNSON, of Gloucester, Ontario, as members of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Polar Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
